d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e379864e64d9a7b28ee5aa22acc80ad18c876b","tid":86453,"uid":63009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&quot;我覺得呢個係最worst既情况囉...&quot; --&amp;gt; 點解唔可以講&quot;最差&quot;，而要夾硬講&quot;最worst&quot;?<br />\n&quot;我人生最大既goal係...&quot; --&amp;gt; 班港女係咪連小學中文詞語&quot;目標&quot;都唔識?<br />\n&quot;個professor好charm啊，但係有少少harsh...&quot; --&amp;gt; 屌你一係成句英文啦，又中又英聽到人好撚攰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我忍左好撚耐<br />\n乜撚野好charm...<br />\n係charming<br />\n<br />\nYou never say &quot;he's very charm&quot; you say &quot;he's very charming&quot;<br />\nThe only time you use charm is &quot;I'm attracted by his charms&quot;<br />\nOther than that... you would say use charm as a noun.. such as &quot;nice charm you're wearing on your neck&quot;"},{"pid":"7b21f748d5e86a800d3013862f9fd01a5f197137","tid":86453,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:58:53.000Z","msg":"Sorry我係講野中英夾雜<br />\n咪當面屌柒我囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06eb9671d36f5da87b6cf2bb640e944c7053b200","tid":86453,"uid":26179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"其實有時中英夾雜真係會表達得好啲，始終世上冇一種完美嘅語言，中英夾雜更加係港式粵語獨有嘅文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有啲聽得出係夾硬加英文嘅真係好撚肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說以前試過做group project，嗰組人明明全部都係local，得一個叫做所謂名校出生，雖然都冇咩關系架啦，屌你班臭港女開會嗰陣可以全程用英文傾但係又表達唔到個idea<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扮乜撚野唧講中文好失禮你呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">利申唔敢屌佢地，但係啲英文好過佢地十七條街咁上吓</span></span>"},{"pid":"274bf02a1f779a24c7aae9c199039d5fb3a8e8be","tid":86453,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:59:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">肥婆黎</span>"},{"pid":"8f42ac898525fc7ebfc197489f01c33681d7a1ad","tid":86453,"uid":73240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:02:22.000Z","msg":"最憎人講好charm<br />\n廣東話入面 '好' 係會用形用詞去跟<br />\neg好靚， 好蠢<br />\n但charm係 verb or noun<br />\neg<br />\nHe was charmed(v)  by her good looks<br />\nHe has an irresistable charm(n)<br />\n<br />\n要用嘅唔該一係就話<br />\n佢好charming呀<br />\n咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190946cc6f3466e8e0e0104352d069ae16bc6e2c","tid":86453,"uid":73240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&quot;我覺得呢個係最worst既情况囉...&quot; --&amp;gt; 點解唔可以講&quot;最差&quot;，而要夾硬講&quot;最worst&quot;?<br />\n&quot;我人生最大既goal係...&quot; --&amp;gt; 班港女係咪連小學中文詞語&quot;目標&quot;都唔識?<br />\n&quot;個professor好charm啊，但係有少少harsh...&quot; --&amp;gt; 屌你一係成句英文啦，又中又英聽到人好撚攰</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我忍左好撚耐<br />\n乜撚野好charm...<br />\n係charming<br />\n<br />\nYou never say &quot;he's very charm&quot; you say &quot;he's very charming&quot;<br />\nThe only time you use charm is &quot;I'm attracted by his charms&quot;<br />\nOther than that... you would say use charm as a noun.. such as &quot;nice charm you're wearing on your neck&quot;</blockquote><br />\nfuck,  慢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0612a99e974452c5ff718959e1f961f647494754","tid":86453,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:06:15.000Z","msg":"港大仔女都係天之驕子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講野好有特色"},{"pid":"f9c1361c640d5e3e32c0650c02ab7bb00d179795","tid":86453,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>識有個朋友，六歲