ther than that... you would say use charm as a noun.. such as &quot;nice charm you're wearing on your neck&quot;</blockquote><br />\nfuck,  慢左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要<br />\n其實好開心唔係得我一個咁諗<br />\n個個都覺得冇問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係一種好特別既現象喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正如英文都唔會有你fake我呢種用法</blockquote><br />\n你有冇睇晒我地講乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n Charm係noun唔係verb咁用呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n話要用嘅用charming呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思係一種好特別既現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得香港會咁"},{"pid":"ed42d1a0aa4a26845156840799557a2fa06fd82e","tid":86453,"uid":73371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:58:24.000Z","msg":"薄大講<br />\n好Champ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8338d77f962a7c1954d34aa5c024e7fc34d964","tid":86453,"uid":63009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T11:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n Charm係noun唔係verb咁用呀嘛</blockquote><br />\n話要用嘅用charming呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我明呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我意思係一種好特別既現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得香港會咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為 你fake我 都係錯<br />\n轉做英文係 you fake me<br />\n但係正確講法係you faked me out<br />\nAnother example would be: I got faked out by him <br />\nFake out 好多時nba會用 例如curry faked out a 3pointer to make a pass"},{"pid":"90df481adc6c41e6caf3b03cdafac3219bddcdcf","tid":86453,"uid":68389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:48:01.000Z","msg":"有日搭巴士聽到個老豆不停又中又英咁同個仔講野 講到成車都聽到 煩到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2d02c63f4360bc90f1f7f87e021a2437